detail.name: Spiko EU T-Bills Money Market Fund
detail.public_notice: According to GoPlus, this is a proxy contract. The contract owner can make code changes to the token contract including but not limited to disabling sells, changing fees, minting, transferring tokens etc. Exercise caution.

description.en: Spiko EU T-Bills Money Market Fund is a fully-licensed EUR money market fund operating under the EU regulatory framework. It only invests in Treasury Bills issued by the strongest Eurozone Member States with less than 6 months maturity and keeps its maximum average portfolio maturity under 2 months.
